org.gvsig.derivedgeometries.swing.api.panels

Interface FeaturesControlPanel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultFeaturesControlPanel

    public interface FeaturesControlPanel
extends Component
    Features control panel contains three panels. First panel shows information about source layer and output layer. Second panel shows information of source layer features and the last panel permits users to add, remove and order selected features to create derived geometries.
